# grapher_trace_smoke.numos — open Grapher, commit y=x, plot it, enter Trace mode,
# reveal the crosshair + value pill, screenshot, and ASSERT Grapher is active.
#
# Phase 8N smoke (warning-only candidate; NO golden, NO mask in this phase).
# Exercises Grapher Trace mode on a plotted y=x.
#
# Flow (all verified in src/apps/GrapherApp.cpp):
#   * The Graph tab opens already in TRACE mode (switchTab GRAPH first entry sets
#     _grMode=TRACE, GrapherApp.cpp:781), but the first replot is deferred and no
#     trace overlay is drawn until a trace key runs.
#   * `right` (handleGraphTrace, GrapherApp.cpp:2491-2508) advances the trace cursor
#     and calls syncViewportToCursor (GrapherApp.cpp:1981-1999) -> replot() rasterizes
#     grid+axes+curve into the native buffer, and the handler ends with
#     drawTraceCursor (GrapherApp.cpp:1667) which shows the crosshair + floating value
#     pill ("x: .. y: ..") + info-bar readout ("Trace: x=.. y=..").
#   * computePOIs runs an async 10ms POI timer (GrapherApp.cpp:2695-2716); in
#     --deterministic mode it fires by frame index and settles within ~2 ticks, so the
#     captured frame is stable and byte-identical run-to-run after a generous wait.
#
# y=x is required because GraphModel only treats an expression as a valid function if
# it contains "=" (getExprRHS, GraphModel.cpp:28-36); bare "x" would not plot.
#
# Tofu: the trace value pill (_tracePillLabel) previously used stix_math_18, which has
# no U+0020 glyph, so its "x: .. y: .." text tofu'd at the spaces. Phase 8N switches
# only that one plain-prose pill label to lv_font_montserrat_14 (GrapherApp.cpp:647);
# the info-bar readout was already montserrat (Phase 8J). Curve, grid, axes, tick
# labels, and graph math are unchanged.
#
# Determinism: run1-vs-run2 from fresh launches is byte-identical (the trace body —
# curve, crosshair, pill, and info-bar readout — is fully deterministic on the same
# binary). The only wall-clock-volatile region is the StatusBar clock (HH:MM).
#
# All key tokens are already scriptable (down, enter, y, =, x, graph, right) — no
# NativeHal change is required.
#
# Timing notes (deterministic, step-ms 16):
#   * 200 frames -> splash done; launcher.
#   *  60 frames -> Grapher load + fade settles.
#   *   6 keys   -> commit y=x (down, enter, y, =, x, enter).
#   *  80 frames -> expression committed/settled.
#   *   1 key    -> graph (createGraphPanel; TRACE mode; replot deferred).
#   * 120 frames -> Graph panel created + LVGL layout pass computed.
#   *   1 key    -> right (replot + drawTraceCursor reveals crosshair + value pill).
#   * 180 frames -> replot + async POI timer settle + screen settles.
#
# Run:
#   program --headless --deterministic --script tests/emulator/scripts/grapher_trace_smoke.numos \
#           --frames 800 --screenshot out/grapher_trace_smoke.ppm --quiet
# Exit codes: 0 ok · 2 script/parse error · 3 screenshot write error · 4 assertion failure.

log "grapher_trace_smoke: waiting for launcher"
wait 200

# Open Grapher (emulator launchApp id 1 — same id as the launcher's Grapher card).
open_app Grapher
wait 60

# Commit the plottable function y=x into the first slot. Sequence:
#   down  : TAB_BAR -> CONTENT (Add row, _numFuncs=0)
#   enter : addFunction() -> startEditing() slot 0
#   y = x : insertVariable('y'), insertVariable('='), insertVariable('x')
#   enter : commit -> stopEditing(); function parsed and marked valid
key down
key enter
key y
key =
key x
key enter
wait 80

# Switch to the Graph tab (TRACE mode by default; first replot is deferred).
key graph
wait 120

# Advance the trace cursor once: triggers the first replot (curve) AND reveals the
# crosshair + floating value pill via drawTraceCursor.
key right
wait 180

# Screenshot FIRST: the deferred capture happens on this frame, before the assert
# runs on a later frame, so the artifact is produced even if the assertion fails.
screenshot out/grapher_trace_smoke.ppm
log "grapher_trace_smoke: screenshot captured"

assert_app Grapher
log "grapher_trace_smoke: assertion passed (Grapher active, Trace mode)"
